Individual and Society: The nicest prof in my first year. If you hate reading don't bother with this course; 80-100pgs per week but it's all for discussion not tested except for some key ideas on the midterm. The readings are dense but he does a great job of clarifying. He made us all brownies on the last day. I cant stress how kind-hearted he is.
